issues.message: Rename event handler "Show_completion_list_after_a_character_is_deleted_Checked" to match the regular expression: "^(([a-z][a-z0-9]*)?([A-Z]{1,3}[a-z0-9]+)*([A-Z]{2})?_)?([A-Z]{1,3}[a-z0-9]+)*([A-Z]{2})?$".

Rename event handler "Show_completion_list_after_a_character_is_deleted_Unchecked" to match the regular expression: "^(([a-z][a-z0-9]*)?([A-Z]{1,3}[a-z0-9]+)*([A-Z]{2})?_)?([A-Z]{1,3}[a-z0-9]+)*([A-Z]{2})?$".
